&lt;li&gt;Must be tech-savvy and comfortable with the usage of general business software&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self-starter mindset&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to travel between multiple office locations as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An interest in client services and relationship-building&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to prioritize and multitask&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent written and verbal communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong attention to detail&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong organizational skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
