&lt;p&gt;The Agency is a global, boutique real estate brokerage representing a portfolio of properties across the world’s prime markets and celebrated destinations. The Agency is one of the fastest-growing luxury, boutique brands in the world. Our clients and agents benefit from our international team across in-house creative, public relations and technology. The Agency has closed more than $104 billion in real estate transactions since 2011, comprising over 150+ offices in 15 countries and counting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experienced Real Estate Agent – The Agency New York&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Agency New York is built for experienced real estate agents — and accomplished full-time professionals making a smart second-career move — who are ready to grow faster, think bigger, and elevate their presence in the market. This isn’t a place to maintain the status quo — it’s where ambitious professionals come to compete and win in one of the world’s most competitive real estate arenas.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Joining The Agency means becoming part of a global community of high-performing professionals who value collaboration, mentorship, and doing business at the highest level. With in-house marketing and PR support, your listings — and your name — gain meaningful visibility where it matters most. You’ll work alongside driven, collaborative agents who share insights, celebrate wins, and consistently push each other forward.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As part of a global network spanning 150+ offices across 15 countries, you’ll tap into powerful referral opportunities and international connections. Our agent-to-staff support ratio is among the strongest in New York City, and many of our agents double—or even triple—their production with the resources and support we provide.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We Offer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Elite Mentorship &amp;amp; Coaching – &lt;/strong&gt;Weekly coaching and direct access to experienced leadership, supported by one of the highest agent-to-staff ratios in NYC&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business Growth Resources – &lt;/strong&gt;Advanced training, brand-building tools, and personalized marketing support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborative Culture – &lt;/strong&gt;A high-achieving, partnership-driven environment where agents truly support one another&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Global Reach – &lt;/strong&gt;Exclusive referral opportunities and connections across our international network&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bespoke Listing Marketing – &lt;/strong&gt;Full-service listing support, global syndication, and signature branding that elevates every pitch&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Smart, Scalable Tools – &lt;/strong&gt;Technology and systems designed to help you work smarter and grow faster&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An active NY real estate license holder with completed transactions, or a successful full-time professional ready to build a results-driven real estate career&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skilled in managing deals and cultivating client relationships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategic, entrepreneurial, and committed to meaningful growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Polished communicator with a client-first mindset&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compensation&lt;/strong&gt;: This is a 1099 independent contractor position. Compensation is 100% commission-based with no base salary or hourly wage. Commission splits and earning potential vary based on production and individual agreements with the brokerage.&lt;/p&gt;
